## Overview
Exploited XSS in an HTML attribute context by breaking out of quotes and injecting an event handler.

## Key Concept
User input was placed inside an HTML attribute:
<input value="user_input">

## Exploitation Steps
1. Broke out of attribute using "
2. Injected event handler:
   " onmouseover="alert(1)
3. Triggered alert by hovering

## Insight
Even when <script> is blocked, attribute-based injection can lead to execution.
